{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 25,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even before, you know, that-- before the end of the war, when the Russians were coming, you know, they were taking everybody out of the-- of the camp, of Birkenau and Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to-- to go-- going walking at night in 25 below 0.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Always I said, oh, beautiful Athens with the sunshine, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you have it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it started with what's his name--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well I started this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why I forgot his name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have to find the name first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Jesus, I know him for 50 years, 60.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's from Sky Broadcasting Company, you know, the [INAUDIBLE] guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Anyhow, he told me he wanted to do the documentary on me alone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I thought-- and that time was the time that they went was the-- the war in Czechoslov-- in the Czech-- around that part.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So and he said to me, I'll write the script and everything else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it took two years before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I told him, if you want to do it, I'll do it, but you have to take my two cousins, because whatever I don't remember, maybe they will remember.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we did the documentary, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was mostly pretty good at remembering.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time my memory was even much better than now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's 1999. 1990-- before-- '97. '99 we started doing it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was pretty good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think they, you know that they-- they did a lot of good job on this documentary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think a lot of people who told me [? saw ?] them.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
